@startuml
' Диаграмма последовательности для команды parakeet-install
title Выполнение полного цикла установки (configure -> build -> install)

actor Пользователь as User
participant "ParakeetCLI" as CLI
participant "ConfigManager" as Config
participant "KernelConfigurator" as Conf
participant "KernelBuilder" as Build
participant "KernelInstaller" as Inst
participant "BootDevice" as Dev

User -> CLI: parakeet-install
activate CLI

CLI -> Config: load_config(path)
activate Config
Config --> CLI: config object
deactivate Config

CLI -> Conf: configure(linux_dir, backup_dir)
activate Conf
Conf -> Conf: backup old .config
Conf -> Conf: run make nconfig (interactive)
Conf --> CLI: OK
deactivate Conf

CLI -> Build: build(linux_dir, jobs)
activate Build
Build -> Build: make bzImage modules -jN
Build --> CLI: build successful
deactivate Build

CLI -> Inst: install(config, devices)
activate Inst

Inst -> Inst: create temp directory
Inst -> Inst: make install & genkernel to temp

loop for each flash device
    Inst -> Dev: new BootDevice(device, partition, mountpoint)
    activate Dev
    Inst -> Dev: mount()
    Inst -> Dev: copy_kernel_files(temp_dir)
    Inst -> Dev: update_grub()
    Inst -> Dev: install_grub()
    Inst -> Dev: umount()
    deactivate Dev
end

Inst -> Inst: make modules_install
Inst --> CLI: installation complete
deactivate Inst

CLI --> User: report success / errors
deactivate CLI
@enduml
